      "review_summary": "The branch rewrites Model Aliases prompt guidance and adjusts `sessions_spawn` model override resolution/tests so slash-form aliases can resolve while configured provider/model refs are intended to pass through.\n\nPR surface: Source +17, Tests +61. Total +78 across 4 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. source-level. Current main and `v2026.6.10` still render the reported Model Aliases guidance, and the current `sessions_spawn` resolver passes slash overrides through before alias lookup; I did not run a deterministic live provider-swap scenario because final tool choice depends on model behavior after reading the prompt.",
